subject: Performance issues in executing JUnit Test Cases in AIX
msgSnippet: Hi Team, I am executing JUnit Test Cases using Ant Script in AIX environment. In the AIX environment it is taking 71 minutes for the execution at the same time
messageBody:
Hi Team,

I am executing JUnit Test Cases using Ant Script in AIX environment.
In the AIX environment it is taking 71 minutes for the execution at
the same time same set of scripts are taking 6 minutes in Windows
environment

Regards,
Clement
